{"id":53,"title":"问：如果让你实现一个并发安全的计数器（Counter），支持并发环境下多个goroutine对计数值增减，你会怎么做？","slug":"问：如果让你实现一个并发安全的计数器（Counter），支持并发环境下多个goroutine对计数值增减，你会怎么做？-1766595050","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：有几种方式可以实现线程安全的计数器：最直接的是使用互斥锁（**`**sync.Mutex**`**）保护计数变量，在每次更新前先**`**Lock()**`**，更新后**`**Unlock()**`**，确保同一时刻只有一个goroutine修改计数值。另一种方法是使用Go的原子操作**（`sync/atomic`包），例如`atomic.AddInt64`来对计数值进行原子地增减，这样在底层CPU指令层面保证了并发安全，无需显式加锁。如果计数结果需要跨多个goroutine传递，也可以考虑用**channel**将增减请求发送到单一goroutine串行处理。这几种方法各有应用场景：锁机制代码清晰适用于低频更新，原子操作开销更小适合高频计数，channel串行化适用于更复杂的并发逻辑。无论哪种，实现的要点是**避免竞态条件**，确保临界区操作互斥进行。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.309981+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.309981+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-8091-bd0b-da6d2e3a2d7b","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":53,"blog_post_id":53,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.606734+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.606734+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.309981+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.309981+08:00"}